title: Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs) Logo
description: A circular logo featuring 17 colorful segments, each representing one of the United Nations Sustainable Development Goals (SDGs). The colors range from green, blue, red, orange, to purple, arranged in a way that forms a complete circle, symbolizing unity and the interconnectedness of the goals.

title: Open-Pit Mine
description: An aerial view of an open-pit mine, showcasing multiple layers of excavated earth and rock. The mine features a large, circular pit with steep walls, and a body of water at the bottom. Surrounding the pit are various roads and pathways used for mining operations, with vegetation visible in the background.

title: Monument in a Public Park
description: A large, ornate monument featuring a tall column topped with a statue. The monument is surrounded by sculptures and decorative elements, with two prominent statues on either side. The setting includes lush greenery and palm trees, under a clear blue sky.
